<style type="text/css">
  body {
    background-color: #fff;
  }
  h1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6 {
        font-family: "Lato", sans-serif !important;
  }
</style>
<!-- First Grid -->
<div class="w3-row-padding w3-padding-64 w3-container">
  <div class="w3-content">
    <div class="w3-twothird">
      <h1>What we are and what Apex does?</h1>
      <h5 class="w3-padding-32">Apex Financial Technology Limited is a UK based startup building market risk management, pricing and reporting systems. Our flagship system is called APEX and is targeted to corporate treasury and risk managers.</h5>

      <p class="w3-text-grey">APEX stores all forex, commodity and interest rate trades executed by the company in one place. APEX can price all derivative structures from linear swaps and forwards, vanilla options, option strategies and exotic options. There is a scenario planning module which allows the user to stress the trade, or portfolio of trades, to underlying price and volatility moves. All market data is downloaded and stored in the system. Reporting modules allows customized, complex and multi-dimensional reports to be generated. APEX is a complete trade management system for treasury departments.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="w3-third w3-center">
      <i class="fa fa-area-chart w3-padding-64 apex_chart_color"></i>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- Second Grid -->
<div class="w3-row-padding w3-light-grey w3-padding-16 w3-container">
  <div class="w3-content">
    <div class="container">
      <div id="loginbox" style="margin-top:25px;" class="mainbox col-md-6 col-md-offset-3 col-sm-8 col-sm-offset-2">
          <div class="panel panel-info">
              <div class="panel-heading">
                  <div class="panel-title">Sign In</div>
                  <!-- <div style="float:right; font-size: 80%; position: relative; top:-10px"><a href="#">Forgot password?</a></div> -->
              </div>
              <div style="padding-top:30px" class="panel-body">
                  <div style="display:none" id="login-alert" class="alert alert-danger col-sm-12"></div>
                  <%= form_for(resource, as: resource_name, :html => { :id => "loginform", :class => "form-horizontal", :role => "form" }, url: session_path(resource_name)) do |f| %>
                    <div style="margin-bottom: 25px" class="input-group">
                      <span class="input-group-addon"><i class="glyphicon glyphicon-user"></i></span>
                      <%#= f.label :email %>
                      <%= f.email_field :email, autofocus: true, class: "form-control", placeholder: "Login email *", required: "" %>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div style="margin-bottom: 25px" class="input-group">
                      <span class="input-group-addon"><i class="glyphicon glyphicon-lock"></i></span>
                      <%#= f.label :password %>
                      <%= f.password_field :password, autocomplete: "off", class: "form-control", placeholder: "Password *", required: ""  %>
                    </div>

                    <% if devise_mapping.rememberable? -%>
                      <div class="input-group">
                        <div class="checkbox">
                          <%= f.label :remember_me do %><%= f.check_box :remember_me %> Remember me<% end %>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    <% end -%>

                    <div style="margin-top:10px; margin-left: 0px;" class="form-group">
                      <%= f.submit "Log in", class: "btn btn-success" %>
                    </div>
                  <% end %>
                  
                  <div class="form-group">
                    <div class="col-md-12 control">
                      <div style="border-top: 1px solid#888; padding-top:15px; font-size:85%">
                          New Candidate!
                          <a href="/signup"><%#= render "devise/shared/links" %> Register Here</a>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
              </div>
          </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>


